  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to determine the efficacy and the satisfaction/adaptability of the manual Broscyl速
      toothbrush as compared with a standard &quot; soft &quot; manual toothbrush ADA (American Dental
      Association) reference using the modified Stillman brushing technique, in children, adults
      and elderly persons, after 3 months of daily use.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
